name: Literal Shit.
description:
This NFT is Literal Shit. It is a fully original photograph taken on a barge in southern U.K. c.~2015[This can be verified with an image reverse search]. No more than 1000 of these shits will exist in an authentic manner.

Owners of this NFT will automatically become members of LitShitDAO. Details of which will become known upon conclusion of sale [28 days after].

DAO members will vote on the next minting. It is our sincere hope that the community always strives to vote in:

A) Fully original photography.
B) Somewhat funny, somewhat gross - It should put people off their dinner, but not keep them up at night.

Socials to follow.
